Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.67,1:30:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,already. And to the person who is\Nresisting it and not giving forth their
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.80,1:30:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all. The day seems very very long.\NThey'll say my god isn't it even
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.36,1:30:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,lunchtime yet? They looked at their\Nwatch 40 times.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.80,1:30:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The way to get beyond of a pain thing is\Nlet go resisting it and 100%
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.15,1:30:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,participation.\NIf you're going to haul rocks, then by
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.00,1:30:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God, haul rocks. And you haul rocks as\Nfast as you can haul rocks until you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.48,1:30:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,fall over and the day is so quick. And\Nthat's how you bring forth the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.12,1:30:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of joy at your own existence.\NThe source of joy is the awareness of
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.48,1:31:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the quality and the nature\Nof divinity within you expressing itself
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.92,1:31:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,as life and one's own creation.\NIn reverencing it in others, you
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.19,1:31:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,reverence it in yourself. In re\Nreverencing both in yourself and others,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.80,1:31:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you reverence it for all of mankind.\NWhen consciousness level went from 190
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.23,1:31:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to 207,\Nit's much harder nowadays to be cruel to
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.40,1:31:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people. It's harder. You don't In the\Nold days, cruelty was you all deserved
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.00,1:31:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Now, you know, anything that is\Nnon-intigorous is now called into
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.63,1:31:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,question\Nperhaps overboarding it because the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.23,1:31:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,intellect is pretty dumb.\NThe intellect is trying to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.23,1:31:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,codify it and polit and laws and\Npolitical positions and things but its
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.36,1:31:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,endeavor is in the right direction. It's\Ntrying to correct sources of pain and
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.40,1:32:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,injustice and suffering in the world. In\Nso doing, it's clumsy and stumbles over
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.28,1:32:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and overshoots the mark. But if you see\Nthat behind all that is a kindly even if
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.60,1:32:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,bizarre\Nventation attempts and a
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.84,1:32:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,misinterpretation. See\Nthe willingness to forgive then
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.56,1:32:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,modifies our brain function so that\Nforgiveness becomes automatic. The
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.40,1:32:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,reason it's automatic is because we\Nexperience the world differently than
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.23,1:32:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,other people do. Because we experience\Nthe world differently, we don't see that
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.36,1:32:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there's anything to forgive. Forgive\Nwhat? Everything is just being what it
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.12,1:32:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is. Everything is being what it is.\NSo, we see the jackal eating the hen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.56,1:32:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of getting judgmental about\Nit, oh, bad jackal eating good hen.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.96,1:33:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Good jackal eaten.\NThe jackal folks over here, the hen
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.32,1:33:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,people over here.\NSociety is that way. Jackles and hens.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.92,1:33:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The field itself is the source of one's\Ninner instruction. The mystic is is
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.63,1:33:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,merely one who has learned to look\Nthrough the atheric brain and finesse
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.23,1:33:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the field the answers to that\Nwhich it's it seeks
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.48,1:33:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to merely hold a question. It's like\Nit's like a mudra. One holds the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.52,1:33:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,question like this to divinity unspoken\Nand silently. Divinity knows what the
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.92,1:33:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,question is you're holding\Nand then it tries to find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.56,1:34:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Answer.\NThe purpose of that is to bring it into
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.23,1:34:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the\Nbring it into the linear world for
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.63,1:34:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,purposes of communication.\NOnce you're aware of a thing, it's
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.12,1:34:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,already complete and done. Unless you're\Nwriting about it, lecturing about it, in
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.52,1:34:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which case you want to demonstrate it.\NYeah. So that it is v ver verifiable by
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.92,1:34:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,others because people coming from this\Nfield find the field that we are now
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.67,1:34:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,more familiar with as to be unreal,\Nunreal, not worthy of commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.80,1:34:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you look at whole countries uh that\Ndeny the reality or existence of God, in
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.40,1:34:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,fact it's illegal to mention God. Whole\Ncountries where being loving loving will
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.67,1:34:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,actually get you executed\Nactually get you executed.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.23,1:34:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Southeast Asia, the whole country is\Nthere. To be loving in any way is
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.23,1:35:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,forbidden\Nand it'll get you executed for being
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.32,1:35:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,loving.\NLoving then is of course the biggest
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.19,1:35:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,danger to the ego. So\Nthat which is loving tends to bring up
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.32,1:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is unloving. So you'll also\Nfind people who despise you because
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.63,1:35:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you're kind and loving. Huh?\NSo we brought up the various things can
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.08,1:35:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,happen along the pathway. sudden\Nbreakoff of relationships because you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.52,1:35:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,bring up its opposite and they're\Nunconscious
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.15,1:35:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore the relationship is no\Nlonger compatible.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.63,1:35:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's well known in Alcoholics\NAnonymous that once the person gets
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.92,1:35:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sober and he's no longer the bad guy\Ndependent on her. He becomes autonomous
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.84,1:35:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritually committed that's in the\Nrelationship because being the enabler
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.52,1:36:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,was was her whole trip.\NSo becoming spiritually committed is not
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.56,1:36:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily going to delight everybody\Naround you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.67,1:36:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can accept that that is part of\Nthe price
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.52,1:36:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for thee. Oh Lord, what I lay down all\Nbecause in the end when is faced the
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.04,1:36:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,last remaining thing\Nis the feeling of a personal self.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.76,1:36:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you identify with the essence\Nand source of life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.84,1:36:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end that is the only thing\Nstill standing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.56,1:36:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the knowingness arises. Lay\Ndown even your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.19,1:36:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay down your life and surrender it to\NGod. And then out of the devotion, by
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.00,1:36:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that time the devotion is still\Npowerful. That plus the knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.32,1:37:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you've picked up from the teaching of\Nsomebody who's been there.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.32,1:37:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You literally lay down your life for\NGod.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.71,1:37:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you die\None and only time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.08,1:37:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You do die and you do experience death\Nand it's a moment of agony
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.19,1:37:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and then all splendor shines through\Nshines forth forever more.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.32,1:37:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The death of the ego is the only death\Nyou can experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.88,1:37:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can experience their own death.\NNot possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.36,1:37:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of death is already preset at\Nthe time you're born. The time you're
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.52,1:37:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,born is already a calibratable level of\Nconsciousness. The exact moment of death
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.44,1:37:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is already set at the time you're born.\NWant to reconfirm
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.00,1:37:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that is true.\NReconfirmed every lecture. The exact
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.56,1:38:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,moment is already predetermined. The\Nkarmic said so. The how of it is not
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.84,1:38:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,set.\NThe how of it is not set. The exact
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.11,1:38:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,timing cannot be. You cannot leave an\Ninstant before, nor can you remain an
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.08,1:38:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,instant beyond.\NSo that removes fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.08,1:38:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anytime you think you're dying, that's\Nnot it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.56,1:38:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god. Yeah. If you feel a bullet\Nripping through you, you're not dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.88,1:38:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just agony.\NNo, there's only one death and you'll
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.60,1:38:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,know it. You recognize it's like a high\Npass. It's like a high pass and there's
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.19,1:38:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,no one there except yourself.\NAnd this sense of self
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.96,1:38:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you see arises from the idea that the\Nself is the personal self is the source
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.80,1:39:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of your existence.\NPeople don't realize that it you survive
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.11,1:39:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the field. The ego has you\Nconvinced it's because it watches tra
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.67,1:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,traffic carefully and renews your life\Ninsurance things.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.15,1:39:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Having let all dualities go,\Nhaving surrendered everything to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.63,1:39:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to let go having an\Nopinion, could you let go having
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.56,1:39:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,opinions to God?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.88,1:39:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let go being right to God?\NYep. Would you be willing to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.40,1:39:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThe love of God then brings you to a
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.56,1:39:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,point where you're willing to surrender\Neverything.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.92,1:39:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then with fear you look at life itself.\NThe last remaining
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.60,1:39:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,pin in the bowling alley is standing\Nthere
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.36,1:39:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know that even that has to be\Nsurrendered.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.80,1:40:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness to do it comes out of\Nthe field
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.19,1:40:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because the field of your higher self\Nand this higher self are one and the
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.92,1:40:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,same. So that will finesse it out of the\Nfield.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.23,1:40:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk straight ahead. No matter what\Nis the teaching from Zen
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.04,1:40:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that came up at the time. Walk straight\Nthrough. No matter what. Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.52,1:40:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's trustable at 100.\NThat is trustable at 100.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.00,1:40:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And having lived through it, I stand\Nwitness that it is trustable at 100.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.88,1:40:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because at that moment\Nthe memory of the teaching comes back
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.60,1:40:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then much to your surprise\Nthe intensity of one's love for God
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.88,1:40:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,swells up with such enormous power.\NWhere did that come from? You didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.80,1:41:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,consciously love God to that degree. No,\Nbecause you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.63,1:41:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of it all comes to your\Naid.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.56,1:41:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you surrender your life to God.\NAnd sh the marilent the mind is stunned
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.40,1:41:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,silent.\NThe tail end of the ego right before the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.04,1:41:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,radiant shines forth the tail end of the\Ne ego is still in witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.84,1:41:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it enters this new domain as the\Nnew domain opens up the tail end of the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.04,1:41:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing ego goes is struck dumb with\Nawe.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.15,1:41:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The the revelation is so profound the\Nego is struck dumb. It would not presume
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.11,1:41:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to even have a thought in the presence\Nof what is obviously divinity because
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.04,1:41:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity of all existence is what\Nstuns you at first revelation.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.48,1:41:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only its beauty, its oneness,\Nits exquisite gentleness, its infinite
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.11,1:42:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,power.\NIt stuns the mind into silence
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.19,1:42:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and the mind never thinks again\Nwhich leaves you free to just be what
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.56,1:42:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you are. You see what I mean?
